    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc8330000000000b0f9bf",
      "text": " これは漫画・[メイドは恋する蜂谷くん]の英語の[Fan sub]で[TA-DAH!]が使われてるところ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125429,
      "updated": 1777126250
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc7f00000000000b0f9be",
      "text": " 蜂谷くんの妹が、池谷くんの家のメイドの募集に受かった合格通知の用紙を家族に見せてる。",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125362,
      "updated": 1777126220
    },
    {
      "id": "69eccb4b000000000008ba01",
      "text": " 自分の口で[TA-DA!]と言ってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777126220,
      "updated": 1777126220
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc7d90000000000b0f9bd",
      "text": " (ここに出典のリンクを後で追加[vlzs.icon])",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125339,
      "updated": 1777125855
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc85c0000000000b0f9c0",
      "text": "  Fan subは違法？載せない(読まない)ほうがいい？    というか公式の英語版があったような。確認して",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125470,
      "updated": 1777125871
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc85c0000000000b0f9c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125470,
      "updated": 1777125470
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc75b0000000000b0f9bb",
      "text": "> /* [Hello World Extension] | Get started */  [* Load an unpacked extension] ...... 3. Click the Load unpacked button and select the extension directory. ...... [Ta-da!] The extension has been successfully installed. If no extension icons were included in the manifest, a generic icon will be created for the extension.",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125212,
      "updated": 1777125212
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc75b0000000000b0f9bc",
      "text": " これはChromeの拡張機能開発の公式チュートリアルの序盤にある文章で、PC内のフォルダに学習者が作成した拡張機能をブラウザに読み込むところ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125212,
      "updated": 1777125954
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecc90f0000000000b0f9c4",
      "text": " 無事の読み込めたので[Ta-da!]を鳴らしてお祝いしてる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777125648,
      "updated": 1777125969
